Create a booking

| Given  | When | Then|
| ------------- | ------------- | |
| I add a valid firstname, surname, deposit, checkin, checkout values  | When I select Save  | The details will be displayed on the screen|
| I add a valid firstname  | When I select Save  | The details will not be saved|
| I add a valid surname  | When I select Save  | The details will not be saved|
| I add a valid deposit  | When I select Save  | The details will not be saved|
| I add a valid checkin date  | When I select Save  | The details will not be saved|
| I add a valid checkout date  | When I select Save  | The details will not be saved|

Delete a booking

| Given  | When | Then|
| ------------- | ------------- | |
| There is a booking row  | When I select Delete  | The details will be deleted|

